org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver

Class WaybackAPAuthChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.archive.cdxserver.auth.PrivTokenAuthChecker
      • org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver.WaybackAuthChecker
        • org.archive.wayback.resourceindex.cdxserver.WaybackAPAuthChecker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthChecker

    public class WaybackAPAuthChecker
extends WaybackAuthChecker
    WaybackAuthChecker modified to set up FilenamePrefixFilter from fileIncludePrefixes and fileExcludePrefixes of AccessPoint. This is meant to be used with CompositeAccessPoint to use different prefix filters for different collections. Needs APContextAuthToken to be passed to createAccessFilter(AuthToken).
    See Also:
    EmbeddedCDXServerIndex.createAuthToken(org.archive.wayback.core.WaybackRequest, String)
